39:37.250 --> 39:38.333
Your wife is right.

39:39.583 --> 39:41.375
It's the right thing to do.

39:42.625 --> 39:44.625
We're going to call him tomorrow.

39:44.625 --> 39:49.291
And you are going to become best friends...

39:50.458 --> 39:52.375
with Auguste Dupin.

39:55.916 --> 39:56.750
[Leo groans]

40:03.291 --> 40:05.750
- Long night?
- Yeah. Sorry.

40:06.833 --> 40:09.416
[grunting] It got away from me.

40:12.708 --> 40:14.125
How is your nose?

40:14.125 --> 40:15.208
Sore.

40:16.416 --> 40:17.458
It's okay, though.

40:17.458 --> 40:20.750
[groans] You find that little fucker yet?

40:21.875 --> 40:24.166
Nah, I'm sure she's around here somewhere.

40:25.000 --> 40:29.208
Listen, I know you've been through a lot
and I know what I signed up for.

40:29.208 --> 40:32.000
