40:32.000 --> 40:34.291
[Leo] Don't complain about the drugs.

40:35.583 --> 40:37.500
- It's getting to be a thing.
- [sighs]

40:40.750 --> 40:41.833
Don't do it, Jules.

40:41.833 --> 40:46.000
