I... I want some drugs.

42:00.208 --> 42:03.291
I'm going through a rough time,
and Morrie, you know, well...

42:03.291 --> 42:05.125
Morrie, she's melted, you know.

42:05.125 --> 42:07.458
It turns out she has
this burner phone, and...

42:08.166 --> 42:11.666
