52:40.083 --> 52:41.083
How are you feeling?

52:42.041 --> 52:43.083
Fine.

52:45.666 --> 52:47.583
- How's your leg?
- It's fine.

52:47.583 --> 52:50.416
I was thinking, though.

52:50.416 --> 52:54.333
What if I backed off the Ligodone
for a bit?

52:56.708 --> 52:58.791
- Why?
- I don't know. Just been reading.

52:58.791 --> 53:01.166
I mean, I love it. I do. I just thought...

53:02.208 --> 53:04.875
Maybe see how I go without it
for a few days.

53:04.875 --> 53:06.375
Darling, how would that look?

53:06.875 --> 53:09.583
Besides, you're the proof positive.

53:09.583 --> 53:13.291
You're a walking rebuttal
to all those assholes out there.

53:14.166 --> 53:18.250
You've taken more Ligodone
than just about anybody I know,

53:18.250 --> 53:19.458
and look at you.

53:19.458 --> 53:22.083
- You're a vision. You're...
- [chuckles]

53:22.083 --> 53:24.458
You're thriving. You're pain-free.

53:25.750 --> 53:31.166
You are my most beautiful, perfect proof.

53:36.166 --> 53:39.416
You know, I could use a little cheering up
now you mention it.

53:55.208 --> 53:56.208
What do you say?

54:04.833 --> 54:05.958
[gasps]

54:13.583 --> 54:14.916
[breathing heavily]

54:14.916 --> 54:16.541
[glass breaking]

54:17.250 --> 54:18.375
[Juno] What's wrong?

54:19.625 --> 54:20.625
Roddie!

54:21.666 --> 54:23.875
- Roddie, Roddie, what's wrong?
- [breathing heavily]

54:23.875 --> 54:24.958
Roddie!

54:25.958 --> 54:26.875
[breath trembling]

54:26.875 --> 54:27.958
What's wrong?

54:29.458 --> 54:30.458
What's wrong?

54:33.125 --> 54:34.666
Excuse us, please.

54:36.125 --> 54:37.125
It's okay.

54:40.375 --> 54:43.291
- She shouldn't have called you.
- Of course she should have.

54:43.291 --> 54:45.291
- It's nothing.
- Don't insult me.

54:49.000 --> 54:50.000
[sighs]

54:50.750 --> 54:53.166
Doc came by a few nights ago to the house.

54:54.041 --> 54:55.291
Unannounced.

54:55.291 --> 54:56.625
And what is it?

55:02.125 --> 55:02.958
CADASIL.

55:05.916 --> 55:07.708
- Same as Mom.
- Okay.

55:12.458 --> 55:13.416
And that's, uh...

55:15.041 --> 55:17.458
That's five years on the outside.

55:18.083 --> 55:19.500
It's pretty advanced, so...

55:21.791 --> 55:22.875
It's less. Much less.

55:23.916 --> 55:27.000
You know, I knew vascular dementia
can cause hallucinations,

55:27.000 --> 55:28.500
but I just didn't think...

55:30.416 --> 55:32.166
- And nothing like this.
- Okay.

55:34.208 --> 55:35.125
Victorine.

55:35.125 --> 55:36.791
Yeah, I thought the same thing.

55:37.916 --> 55:40.666
If her contraption really works,
it could buy some time.

55:41.250 --> 55:43.958
Prevent the strokes.
Mitigate the brain damage.

55:43.958 --> 55:45.083
Good. Meds?

55:45.083 --> 55:46.458
Beta-blockers, Risperdal.

55:46.458 --> 55:50.250
Risperdal? He wants you on antipsychotics,
I'll rip his fucking throat out.

55:50.250 --> 55:52.041
Might do, frankly.

55:53.208 --> 55:57.541
I mean, tonight, what I saw,
I mean, what I saw.

55:57.541 --> 56:02.083
Victorine will get her little
heart miracle working first order.

56:05.458 --> 56:07.208
- Same as Mom.
- Stop.

56:22.333 --> 56:24.000
- Hey, what's all that...
- [thudding]

56:24.958 --> 56:26.916
[thudding intensifies]

56:46.166 --> 56:47.166
[Julius] Hey.

56:48.583 --> 56:49.583
Hey!

56:50.333 --> 56:52.541
Almost got her! [grunting]

56:53.083 --> 56:54.000
Shit!

56:54.500 --> 56:55.583
[yells]

56:56.916 --> 56:58.208
Leo, what's happening?

56:58.208 --> 57:00.666
[Leo grunting]

57:00.916 --> 57:02.958
- [frame crashes]
- If she runs, grab her!

57:02.958 --> 57:05.416
[grunting]

57:05.416 --> 57:07.291
I'm gonna flatten that cunt, I swear!

57:07.291 --> 57:08.625
[grunting]

57:17.791 --> 57:19.041
[yells]

57:19.041 --> 57:21.500
Come here! [grunts]

57:26.583 --> 57:27.500
[snarling]

57:27.500 --> 57:29.000
[screaming]

57:29.000 --> 57:30.250
What?

57:32.541 --> 57:34.166
[Leo breathing heavily]

57:34.166 --> 57:35.250
You don't see it?

58:07.208 --> 58:08.625
Stop! Stop!

58:11.791 --> 58:12.791
[body thuds]

58:33.375 --> 58:35.083
[cars honking]

58:43.750 --> 58:45.750
[cat meowing softly]

58:59.625 --> 59:01.625
[sirens approaching]
